values: Word on the street is that this new Rubin guy the band hired to produce the album has a little thing for my Bri-Bri.  I must admit, i can't really blame him but still, he had better back off or he'll never be able to shop again in this city!
Today was a bit of a sad day, no shopping was done.  I really need to have a talk with that Rivers guy, who does he think he is taking up all of our shopping time? Pfft album five, whatev.
All things are well, here in the land of Bell. Brian and i did some shopping on evening last, shoes were purchased and a good time was had by all.
